title: 8 - What is the Meaning of ProLife
description:
In this episode, we discuss the shooting at a Colorado Planned Parenthood clinic and how Jesus might challenge the pro-life crowd.  As always, please leave your thoughts and questions in the comments below!

- Mike Erre
